  "body": "# Description\r\n\r\nWhile researching disabling of Whisper on our fleets don in https://github.com/status-im/infra-eth-cluster/issues/32#issuecomment-674950824 I found out that there is a tiny number of nodes that run most recent version(`1.5.0`) but use only Whisper without Waku. I think it's about time that we disable Whisper and remove ability to disable Waku in advanced settings:\r\n![status_advanced_settings](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2212681/90420515-5dc4bc00-e0b8-11ea-920a-8a12bdd440c6.jpg)\r\n\r\n# Reasoning\r\n\r\n* Supporting of Whisper will increase probability of weird bugs popping up\r\n* Whisper has a negative effect on bandwith used on mobile devices\r\n* Narrowing down settings to only waku will simplify Waku node setup",
